flowchart LR
  %% dvn-workshop-maio — Arquitetura (conforme este repositório)
  %% Render no GitHub/VS Code: Mermaid

  Repo[(GitHub Repository<br/>code + manifests)]
  Repo -->|push/merge| GA[GitHub Actions<br/>CI]

  subgraph TF[Terraform (IaC)]
    TF0[00-remote-backend-stack-ai<br/>S3 state (lab)]:::tf
    TF1[01-networking-stack-ai<br/>VPC + subnets + NAT]:::tf
    TF2[02-eks-stack-ai<br/>EKS + Node Group + addons + ECR]:::tf
    TF3[03-ci-cd-stack-ai<br/>OIDC + IAM Role (GitHub)]:::tf
    TF0 --> TF1 --> TF2 --> TF3
  end

  subgraph AWS[AWS Account]
    State[(S3 Remote Backend<br/>Terraform state)]:::aws
    TF0 --> State

    OIDC[OIDC Provider<br/>GitHub → AWS]:::aws
    Role[IAM Role<br/>(AssumeRoleWithWebIdentity)]:::aws
    ECR[(Amazon ECR<br/>backend/frontend)]:::aws

    subgraph VPC[VPC (Multi-AZ)]
      Pub[Subnets públicas]:::net
      Priv[Subnets privadas]:::net
      NAT[NAT Gateway]:::net
      Pub --- NAT
      NAT --- Priv

      subgraph EKS[EKS Cluster]
        API[Kubernetes API]:::k8s
        CNI[AWS VPC CNI<br/>(Prefix Delegation)]:::k8s
        NG[Managed Node Group<br/>(Launch Template + t3.micro lab)]:::k8s
        API --- NG
        CNI --- NG

        subgraph NS1[argocd namespace]
          Argo[ArgoCD]:::k8s
        end

        subgraph NS2[default namespace]
          FE[Frontend Deployment]:::k8s --> SFE[Frontend Service]:::k8s
          BE[Backend Deployment]:::k8s --> SBE[Backend Service]:::k8s
        end
      end
    end
  end

  %% CI: build + push image
  GA -->|OIDC login| OIDC
  OIDC --> Role
  Role -->|push images| ECR

  %% GitOps: update tags in kustomization + ArgoCD sync
  GA -->|update image tags<br/>devops-ia-kubernetes/kustomization.yaml| Repo
  Argo -->|sync manifests (GitOps)| Repo
  Argo -->|apply manifests| API

  %% Runtime: image pull happens on nodes/pods
  NG -->|pods pull images| ECR

  classDef tf fill:#f7fafc,stroke:#4a5568,color:#2d3748;
  classDef aws fill:#fffaf0,stroke:#b7791f,color:#744210;
  classDef net fill:#eef6ff,stroke:#2b6cb0,color:#1a365d;
  classDef k8s fill:#f3f0ff,stroke:#6b46c1,color:#322659;
